Package com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_0s

Class Tier0sFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_0s.Tier0sFactory
  • public class Tier0sFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    Tier0sFactory is responsible for creating instances of services contained inside the com.vmware.nsx_policy.infra.tier_0s package and also has the subpackages reference to access respective subpackage services.
